  div(style="max-width: 800px;").container
    div.row
      div.panel.panel-danger.top-buffer
        div.panel-heading
          h3.panel-title
          | 
          a(href="https://fast-ravine-4145.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank") Calorie Buddy
        div.panel-body
          p  
          | From March 2014 through August 2014, I experience a radical transformation.
          | I lost 80 pounds through dieting and daily exercise. As someone who has been overweight
          | most of his life, I can say that this is the biggest accomplishment of my life thus far.
          | Now I want to maintain this lifestyle, and that requires continuing to exercise and of course,
          | maintaining a healthy diet. This webapp helps me calculate the total calorie value of my meal.
          | Right now the values are hardcoded, but my vision includes expanding the webapp to have users
          | and allowing those users to enter their own entries. Code for the site can be found at this 
          a(href="https://github.com/iga82/CalorieBuddy" target="_blank") Git 
          | repo.


