  div(style="max-width: 800px;").container
    div.row
      div.panel.panel-danger.top-buffer
        div.panel-heading
          h3.panel-title Lift Buddy
        div.panel-body
          p 
          | Life Buddy is an Android application that seeks to solve the problem of the lack of a workout app
          | on Android that has a simple user interface. I'm creating the app with two co-workers, one with 
          | Android experience and the other with backend experience. We've tried and installed multiple workout apps, 
          | and have not found anything that lives to the UI experience that an iOS app provides. We have finished
          | the Android UI, but have run into problems trying to save the workout logs to a cloud storage. We've
          | just discovered Couchbase, which seems to handle our use case. Our current efforts are dedicated to
          | building our Couchbase server through Node JS. The Git repo is currently private.

